explanation.details:
ex. textDisallowStart "["



if the text surpasses the boundary and a registered char comes at the start of the next line,

prevent it from going on the next line and continue it on the current.

ex. textOverflowAutoWait true 

  

if true,

whenever text overflows a textbox, the textbox will auto wait.

ex. lvSystem::IsFixedWindowSize()



return true if the window size cannot change (due to ex. OS)

  

return: bool
